Вакансія від 5 березня 2020
IT sales manager
HotelFriend
IT;
50–250 співробітників
Київ
Повна зайнятість.
Досвід роботи від 1 року.
Вища освіта.
Опис вакансії
HotelFriend is a German IT company with the head office based in Berlin and a development office in Kiev. We develop and support our own product- Hotel management system, designed to facilitate all processes of a hotel, and a Mobile Guest App, using which you can not only choose a hotel and book a room, but also order any service inside and outside your hotel in advance.We are looking for an experienced Sales / Business Development Manager to perform inbound and outbound sales activities, contact the clients, qualify opportunities and close the deals to join our team.Необходимые навыки• Experience in selling IT services in the Western markets is a must; • Fluent English; • Knowledge of software development process, modern technologies, project management methodologies and current trends; • Strong analytical skills; • High learning abilities.Предлагаем• Great opportunities for professional growth;• Young, friendly and ambitious team of professionals; • Cozy office in 10 minutes from metro; • Regular team-buildings and corporate parties.Обязанности• Prospect for potential new clients;• Contacting prospects generated by the marketing team, identifying the opportunities and initiating new business with them; • Build and maintain excellent relationship with potential and current clients; • Ensure that data is accurately entered and managed within the company’s CRM; • Participate in pricing the solution/prepare sales materials and proposals; • Working with technical staff and other internal colleagues to meet customer needs;• Handling negotiations and closing the deals; • Develop and maintain potential client database; • Define strategy and achieve sales targets.
